    <div class="container">

        <h2 class="title">Meus Projetos</h2>
        <div class="row">

            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="row g-0 project-card position-relative rounded-1">
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-md-0 p-md-4">
                        <img src="media/img/Projects/movies.png" class="w-100" alt="...">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 p-4 ps-md-0">
                        <h5 class="mt-0">Movies Lib</h5>
                        <p>Uma biblioteca de filmes utilizando uma API, criada em um curso de React. Vale a pena conferir!</p>
                        <a href="https://edupassero.github.io/ep_movies/" class="stretched-link"/>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="row g-0 project-card position-relative rounded-1">
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-md-0 p-md-4">
                        <img src="media/img/Projects/costs.png" class="w-100" alt="...">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 p-4 ps-md-0">
                        @if (english)
                        {
                            <h5 class="mt-0">Costs</h5>
                            <p>A project manager using Json server, created during a React JS course.</p>                            
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <h5 class="mt-0">Projeto Costs</h5>
                            <p>Um gerenciador de projetos usando o Json server, feito em um curso de React JS</p>
                        }
