        </div>
        <div class="row">

            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="row g-0 project-card position-relative rounded-1">
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-md-0 p-md-4">
                        <img src="media/img/Projects/costs.png" class="w-100" alt="...">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 p-4 ps-md-0">
                        
                        @if (english)
                        {
                            <h5 class="mt-0">Validator</h5>
                            <p>An exercise in logic and data handling, this is a form validator made with HTML, CSS and JS</p>
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <h5 class="mt-0">Validator</h5>
                            <p>Um exercício de lógica e tratamento de dados, é um formulário com validação feito com HTML, CSS e JavaScript</p>
                        }
                        <a href="https://edupassero.github.io/ep_movies/" class="stretched-link" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="row g-0 project-card position-relative rounded-1">
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-md-0 p-md-4">
                        <img src="media/img/Projects/calculator.png" class="w-100" alt="...">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 p-4 ps-md-0">
                        <h5 class="mt-0">Calculadora</h5>
                        <p>Uma calculadora similar ao modelo da Apple, só que muito mais barata!</p>
                        <a href="https://edupassero.github.io/ep_costs/" class="stretched-link" />
                    </div>
                </div>
